In 2015, Rites of Ash was nominated for the Best Modern Rock Band Wammy award.
In late 2015, Lazzo teamed up with Analytics (vocals, keyboards) to form the synth pop duo Blue Skies and Death.
The group's third single, "Parallel Lines", has been featured on Spotify's official playlists: Discover Weekly, Release Radar, and Indie Electronics.
Their EP, Rearrange, was released on September 19, 2016.
